  "detailed_description": "A way up! is a simple platformer about throwing a rock.<br><br>A story about a meteorite separated from his fellow space stones.<br>Can be painful, relaxing, annoying, satisfying.<br>Someone will say it is easy, someone else it is impossible.<br>Depends on you.<br>Play how you want - slowly, quickly, chaotically or strategically.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play as a meteorite to help it get back to space<br></li><li>Venture vertiacally from magma caves through city up to high skies<br></li><li>Simple, dynamic controls - hold a mouse button over a meteorite and throw it<br></li><li>About 2 hours of gameplay depending (can take much longer)<br></li><li>Intense, engaging sometimes frustrating, yet satisfying<br></li><li>Try to get the best time</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036530/extras/0ab24e25ffa0ae8a0e5395db182dd3e5.poster.avif?t=1588980658\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036530/extras/0ab24e25ffa0ae8a0e5395db182dd3e5.webm?t=1588980658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036530/extras/292d21389c30bb1a4ea7c5c7c7ae6d2d.poster.avif?t=1588980658\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036530/extras/292d21389c30bb1a4ea7c5c7c7ae6d2d.webm?t=1588980658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "A way up! is a simple platformer about throwing a rock.<br><br>A story about a meteorite separated from his fellow space stones.<br>Can be painful, relaxing, annoying, satisfying.<br>Someone will say it is easy, someone else it is impossible.<br>Depends on you.<br>Play how you want - slowly, quickly, chaotically or strategically.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play as a meteorite to help it get back to space<br></li><li>Venture vertiacally from magma caves through city up to high skies<br></li><li>Simple, dynamic controls - hold a mouse button over a meteorite and throw it<br></li><li>About 2 hours of gameplay depending (can take much longer)<br></li><li>Intense, engaging sometimes frustrating, yet satisfying<br></li><li>Try to get the best time</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036530/extras/0ab24e25ffa0ae8a0e5395db182dd3e5.poster.avif?t=1588980658\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036530/extras/0ab24e25ffa0ae8a0e5395db182dd3e5.webm?t=1588980658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036530/extras/292d21389c30bb1a4ea7c5c7c7ae6d2d.poster.avif?t=1588980658\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1036530/extras/292d21389c30bb1a4ea7c5c7c7ae6d2d.webm?t=1588980658\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
